@bryanc wrote:

If your useing testscape look below.
[glow=red,2,300]This will get your levels up![/glow]

TestScape based!!!

~WHAT TO DO~

  1. Open client.java
  2. Goto your commands (search “barrows” or “dragon”)
  3. Add this command there…

else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("madskilzyo") && playerRights >= 2) { addSkillXP(14000000, 0); addSkillXP(14000000, 1); addSkillXP(14000000, 2); addSkillXP(14000000, 3); addSkillXP(14000000, 4); addSkillXP(14000000, 5); addSkillXP(14000000, 6); addSkillXP(14000000, 7); addSkillXP(14000000, 8); addSkillXP(14000000, 9); addSkillXP(14000000, 10); addSkillXP(14000000, 11); addSkillXP(14000000, 12); addSkillXP(14000000, 13); addSkillXP(14000000, 14); addSkillXP(14000000, 15); addSkillXP(14000000, 16); addSkillXP(14000000, 17); addSkillXP(14000000, 18); addSkillXP(14000000, 19); addSkillXP(14000000, 20); addSkillXP(14000000, 21); addSkillXP(14000000, 22); addSkillXP(14000000, 23); addSkillXP(14000000, 24); sendMessage("Enjoy the skills."); }
Feel free to change the message sent but keep the “” and change the command from madskilzyo to maxstats or what ever…

Enjoy
